### ==============================
### AUTH ROUTES
### ==============================

### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "user1@example.com",
  "password": "User1234"
}

### Login as user
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@example.com",
  "password": "User1234"
}

### Login as admin (after running seed)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@demo.com",
  "password": "Admin1234"
}


